headline: Trimble Announces Dimensions Australia, Expanding Access to Flagship User Conference Experience
summary: Trimble (Nasdaq: TRMB) is excited to announce Trimble Dimensions Australia, a new regional user conference taking place August 27-28 in Brisbane, Australia. Tailored for engineering and construction professionals, the conference provides two days of fast-paced education on innovative technology solutions, and dedicated opportunities to connect with peers and product experts.
